Printing pattern "PROGRAM" as right-angled triangle.
P
PR
PRO
PROG
PROGR
PROGRA
PROGRAM

For example:
Result
P
PR
PRO
PROG
PROGR
PROGRA
PROGRAM

Solution :
//Java

import java.util.*;
public class PatternRight {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String str = "PROGRAM";
        char[] arr = str.toCharArray();
        
        for (int i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j <= i; j++) {
                System.out.print(arr[j]);
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}
